scripts.make-models: npx sequelize-cli model:generate --name User --attributes username:string,password:string,partfolio:string,npx sequelize-cli model:generate --name shares --attributes symbol:string,price:integer,lastUpdateAt:time,npx sequelize-cli model:generate --name portfolio --attributes userid:integer quantityofshares:integer,npx sequelize-cli model:generate --name trade --attributes totalsold:integer
